<s> The SGML ERB met today, Oct 17th, and voted on several items already submitted to the SGML WG. Participating: Bosak, Clark, Maler (in part), Magliery (in part), Paoli, Sperberg-McQueen, and Sharpe.  </s>
<s> Absent: Bray, DeRose, Hollander, Kimber, and Connolly.  </s>
<s> All decisions were by consensus of all those participating in the call, and thus carry a majority of the membership of the ERB.  </s>
<s> The text below is substantially the same as the drafts discussed by the ERB, but was edited after the meeting to reflect the ERB's decisions; the ERB has thus not seen and approved the precise wording given, and may choose to correct any editorial errors made in the revision.  </s>
