<s> Well, while I'm on a role, let me clarify things a bit further.  </s>
<s> MIME is a storage manager.  </s>
<s> FSIs are a means of identifying storage managers in an entity declaration.  </s>
<s> So the two work together; they are not alternatives.  </s>
<s> (Actually, the SGML Extended Facilities list two MIME-based storage managers: MIME is a "container" storage manager, like TAR, and is used for normal entity declarations.  </s>
